The paper deals with admission control in networks, which is a problem in computer networks and falls under the category of networked systems (cs.NI). The paper also discusses online algorithms, which are a subfield of algorithms and data structures (cs.DS). The admission control problem is a combinatorial optimization problem, which is a topic in game theory (cs.GT) and algorithms (cs.AL).
